data.description: Looking for that spacious 3 bedroom home? Well you’re in luck because this 3BED/2.5BATH stunner just hit the market with a whopping approximate 2014sqft this home boast a spacious design! Nestle within the well-desired neighborhood of Heartwood Park this HOME, screams elegance and curb appeal, 2017 Stylecraft Build.  Upon entry this home features a large foyer open to an attractive living space, an eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar & walk-in pantry (open to the living area), stainless steel appliances, built-in microwave, a custom backsplash, granite countertops, great entry ways, high-ceilings, separate garden tub & a huge walk-in shower in the primary bathroom, a dual vanity, upstairs utility room with washer & dryer connections (all electric), 2 car garage, decent sized backyard, 6ft privacy fence, front/back/side automatic zoned sprinkler system, covered porch & patio, the list goes on! Don’t miss your opportunity to view this home today call to schedule a showing!  You will fall love with the layout and build quality of this home!
